{
  "_comment": "Wide 100-ticker universe scanned on 5-minute bars via yfinance. Combines the breadth of wide_yfinance with the intraday-tuned thresholds of intraday_5m. IBKR would hit rate limits with this universe; use yfinance only. Remember yfinance 5m bars are ~15 min delayed — fine for building an intraday watchlist, not for live entry timing.",
